# Title: Change Winevt Channel Access Permission Via Registry
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-09-17
# Level: high
# Description: Detects tampering with the "ChannelAccess" registry key in order to change access to Windows event channel.
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1685.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_set/registry_set_change_winevt_channelaccess.yml

Details IN ("*(A;;0x1;;;LA)*", "*(A;;0x1;;;SY)*", "*(A;;0x5;;;BA)*") TargetObject="*\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\WINEVT\\Channels\\*" TargetObject="*\\ChannelAccess" NOT ((Image="*\\TiWorker.exe" Image="C:\\Windows\\WinSxS\\*") OR Image="C:\\Windows\\servicing\\TrustedInstaller.exe")